'''Francisco Nunez''' (February 11, 1955 - April 15, 2023) was a Mexican firefighter. 

==Early Life==
Francisco Nunez was born in February 11 1955 during his parents honeymoon at Guadalajara, Mexico

His Parents we’re named  Eduardo Nunez ( father ) and Lila Nunez ( mother )

He has an older sister named Leticia. When he was age 1, her younger sister was born. Something big happened when he was Age 3, His father died due to esophageal cancer. He started studying at elementary school when he was 6 and went to college to study history when he was 14. He joined social media when he was 15. He graduated college when he was 18. And he failed his driver’s license for the first time

==Career==
He applied as a firefighter when he was 18, He dated Silvia Mendez when he was 23. He tried to apply for a driver’s license but he failed again.

At Age 31, he took his family on a trip to Lisbon Portugal and he got married. His mother retired when he was 36 and his mother kept having babies while he adopted 3 babies. He bought a new car when he was 40 years old. His mother died when he was 45 and attended the funeral. He kept promoting until he was a chief. Silvia retired when he was 67 years old.

==Death==
[[File:Francisco-Nunez.Death.jpg|thumb|Francisco Nunez Death]]
Francisco Nunez died at the age of 68 ( April 15 2023 ) because he had to suffer a stroke. His net worth was $1,926,725. He has been working on a firefighter for 50 years. He has 6 children, 7 grandchildren, his wife, his two sisters attended the funeral. He has been diagnosed with depression from age 61 to death ( 7 years )

